# Next.js 16

Read `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` before writing Next.js code — APIs differ from older versions.

- App Router only: `app/` directory, server components by default
- Client components: add `"use client"` only when needed (interactivity, hooks, browser APIs)
- Use `next/image` for product images; set `width`/`height` or `fill`

# Flipkart UI tokens

- Primary blue: `#2874f0`
- Accent yellow: `#ffe500`
- Product card: image, title (2-line clamp), rating stars, price row (selling + strikethrough MRP + % off)
- Listing page: left filter sidebar + product grid

# Data fetching

- Call backend at `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (default `http://localhost:5000`)
- Prefer server components + `fetch` for catalog pages; client state for cart interactions
